  "remarks": "\nMian Abdul HAQ is a cleric (“Pir”) at Bharchundi Sharif Shrine. HAQ is an involved person under the Global Human Rights Sanctions Regulations 2020 because he\n is or has been responsible for activity that abuses the right not to be subjected to torture or cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment, through his role in the forced conversions and marriages of girls and \nwomen from religious minorities. \n",
